Product Requirements Document (PRD)
CFO.ai — AI Financial Co-Pilot for SMEs

Version: 1.0
Project Type: Frontend MVP (Internship Project)
Program: EDSIP (Enchanted Digital Academy Student Internship Programme)

1. Project Overview
Product Name

CFO.ai

Tagline

Your AI Financial Co-Pilot for Smarter Business Decisions.

Product Vision

CFO.ai is an AI-powered financial management dashboard designed to help Small and Medium-sized Enterprises (SMEs) understand the health of their business beyond account balances.

Unlike traditional banking apps that only show transactions, CFO.ai provides intelligent financial insights, business analytics, AI-generated recommendations, and operational reports to help business owners make smarter decisions.

This project is a frontend-only MVP, using mock data to simulate real business operations. It is designed to expose interns to building a modern SaaS application while collaborating as a frontend engineering team.

2. Problem Statement

Most SME banking applications focus on:

Sending money
Receiving payments
Viewing balances
Transaction history

Business owners, however, need answers to questions such as:

Am I making a profit?
Which customers owe me money?
Can I afford to hire another employee?
Why are my expenses increasing?
Is my business financially healthy?
What should I focus on today?

These insights often require accountants or multiple software tools.

CFO.ai brings everything together in a single intelligent dashboard.

3. Project Objectives

By the end of the project, the team should build a frontend application that enables users to:

Monitor business performance
View financial analytics
Track revenue and expenses
Monitor invoices
View customer insights
Generate business reports
Receive AI-powered financial recommendations
Experience a modern SaaS dashboard
